column16: Kevin Kiermaier singles on a soft line drive to left fielder Moises Sierra.   Brandon Guyer to 2nd.
Mike Moustakas grounds out, second baseman Marcus Semien to first baseman Jose Abreu.
Scott Snodgress intentionally walks Omar Infante.

Eric Hosmer grounds into a force out, first baseman Jose Abreu to shortstop Alexei Ramirez.   Alex Gordon scores.    Salvador Perez out at 2nd.  Eric Hosmer advances to 2nd, on a throwing error by shortstop Alexei Ramirez.
Josh Donaldson singles on a ground ball to left fielder Michael Taylor.   Eric Sogard scores.    Sam Fuld scores.
Josh Reddick flies out to right fielder Avisail Garcia.
Coco Crisp lines out to second baseman Carlos Sanchez.
Sam Fuld singles on a ground ball to shortstop Alexei Ramirez, deflected by second baseman Carlos Sanchez.   Jed Lowrie scores.    Nate Freiman scores.    Eric Sogard to 2nd.
Eric Sogard singles on a line drive to left fielder Michael Taylor.   Derek Norris scores.    Jed Lowrie to 3rd.    Nate Freiman to 2nd.
Nate Freiman singles on a line drive to left fielder Michael Taylor.   Derek Norris to 3rd.    Jed Lowrie to 2nd.
Jed Lowrie reaches on a fielding error by third baseman Marcus Semien.   Derek Norris to 2nd.
Derek Norris singles on a ground ball to left fielder Michael Taylor.
Eduardo Escobar singles on a ground ball to shortstop Alexei Ramirez.   Oswaldo Arcia to 2nd.
Aaron Hicks flies out to center fielder Adam Eaton.
Josmil Pinto lines out to right fielder Avisail Garcia.
Kennys Vargas homers (6) on a line drive to left center field.   Joe Mauer scores.
